<br>
Personally, if I'm soloing low blues and want to keep my pet without reclaiming, I use 53 air pet.  He tanks much better than the others.  If I'm going to be reclaiming and chaining, I use either 51 earth or 50 MS2.  If I'm going to do a straight up fight against something big, I use either my biggest earth or biggest air pet.<br>
<br>
If I'm in a group or agro kiting, I use water.<br>
<br>
You have different pets for different reasons.  Saying that one particular pet is not good for soloing says more about your solo tactics than the pet.<br>
<br>
